metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Canned Heat is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Canned Heat has sections analyzed in the following keys: D Minor,  and E Major.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

The song's amazing outro, which involves a modulation from D minor (the rest of the song) to E major (this outro). Well, to be honest, I think it's in E major but please DO correct me if I'm wrong on that. I hope I got the chords (there's plenty of borrowed ones!) right enough. Enjoy guys!
